The SSP control implementation page still imports the control-implementations StatementByComponent partial, while the guarded fetch change in this branch was applied to src/views/system-security-plans/partials/StatementByComponent.vue, which is only imported by its new test. The live component still builds its component URL from useSystemStore().system.securityPlan?.uuid, so direct navigation with no active SSP can still request /system-security-plans/undefined/... and viewing a non-active SSP can fetch component details from the wrong plan.
